&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;C-146A Wolfhound is the aircraft&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be able to pass a medical/dental physical for deployments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work in a team environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to read engineering drawings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
