&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-8 years of aircraft Maintenance experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working on C-146A Wolfhound aircraft&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
